data.description: Escape to this beautifully updated home in the highly desired neighborhood, Eaglewood in Eagle River.  This home is flooded with natural light and offers stunning views of highland mountain. With an open-concept layout, cozy fireplace, and modern kitchen, it's perfect for both relaxing and entertaining.In the lower level you'll find a second living space, a cozy wood stove, and a fourth bedroom. Enjoy the private, fully fenced in backyard, serene surroundings from the deck, or explore the nearby walking trails. Don't miss out on this opportunity to live in a completely updated home in Eaglewood.
